data.title: Sibling Drive-alry
data.meta_description: Posts about Aselin Debison written by Josh
data.text:
https://longdistancebromance.files.wordpress.com/2014/06/burn-her-couches-iris-the-hapy-professor.mp3

Andy’s back from her trip to London and she tells us all about it.

I guess it wasn’t very much of an interesting trip since she talks for maybe FIFTEEN MINUTES. Seriously guys, if Josh goes to London, he’d come back with stories and talk for days!

I gots stories FO’ DAYS, YO!

Since it’s a condensed episode Josh went “back to the vault” and pulled out an old recording from waaaaaay back in December 2013.

It’s the Internet podcast debut of our good friend Iris.

Hope y’all enjoy it… even those of you in Argentina.
